= **SCP-8607** -- **Pistanthrophobia: [[span style="color: #f1a3e6"]]Lucy's House[[/span]]**
= ◇ //Day 26 of the 2024 SCP "Phobia" Anthology, by [[*user Uncannyon]]// ◇

----

@@ @@

**Content Warning:** This article contains themes related to child abuse

[[include :scp-wiki:info:end]]





